      <title>杜特尔特盟友将重振赌场，开发商由马科斯·金支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/duterte-ally-eyes-casino-partner-in-marcos-kin-backed-builder</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾大亨黄书贤 (Dennis Uy) 正在寻求与一家由与菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯 (Ferdinand Marcos Jr.) 堂兄家族有关联的公司支持的建筑公司合作，以完成这位商人停滞的赌场项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/duterte-ally-eyes-casino-partner-in-marcos-kin-backed-builder</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 04:36:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
