      <title>自特朗普胜选以来，美国比特币 ETF 流入量接近 100 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/us-bitcoin-btc-etf-inflows-near-10-billion-since-trump-election-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自唐纳德·特朗普当选总统以来，已有近 100 亿美元涌入直接投资比特币的美国交易所交易基金，人们押注特朗普对加密货币行业的拥抱将预示着市场繁荣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/us-bitcoin-btc-etf-inflows-near-10-billion-since-trump-election-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 03:56:40 GMT</pubDate>
